OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,FLess than a year after the island went
OL,7,Fto the polls, people in Guernsey will
OL,8,Fsoon be voting again.
OL,10,FThat's because a by-election is being
OL,11,Fheld on Wednesday 29 April with 11
OL,12,Fcandidates up for a single vacant
OL,13,Fposition.
OL,15,FIt's a date that very nearly didn't
OL,16,Fhappen, after politicians debated
OL,17,Fwhether to have a vote at all.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,FThe number of Deputies dropped from 38
OL,7,Fto 37 as Jonathan Le Tocq was jailed
OL,8,Fafter pleading guilty to 15 sexual
OL,9,Foffences, including possessing
OL,10,Fthousands of indecent images.
OL,12,FAnd many deputies argued that if the
OL,13,FStates was operating well with only 37
OL,14,Fwhile Le Tocq was absent, why spend
OL,15,Fthousands on the by-election and pay
OL,16,Ffor another member's salary.
OL,18,FHowever, they decided by 24 votes to
OL,19,F11 to hold one and now the public has
OL,20,F11 names to choose from.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
