OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,FSome have tried to get in before,
OL,7,Fothers are completely new, and several
OL,8,Fwant to return to politics having
OL,9,Fserved in the past.
OL,11,FWe reached out to all of them and
OL,12,Fasked two simple questions: Why are
OL,13,Fyou standing and what are your
OL,14,Fpriorities?
OL,16,FTheir responses are below and appear
OL,17,Fin alphabetical order by surname.
OL,19,FEach candidate also supplied a photo
OL,20,Fwhich will next to their answers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
