CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,FLuke Graham
OL,8,F"I'm standing because Guernsey is
OL,9,Fbeing let down by weak leadership,
OL,10,Fsoft decisions, and a lack of backbone
OL,11,Fwhen it matters most. Too many people
OL,12,Ffeel priced out, overlooked, and
OL,13,Fignored while those in power talk in
OL,14,Fcircles and deliver very little. That
OL,15,Fhas to change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I believe in putting local people
OL,7,Ffirst - in housing, in jobs, and in
OL,8,Fopportunity. We cannot continue down a
OL,9,Fpath where hardworking islanders are
OL,10,Fsqueezed while systems are exploited
OL,11,Fand accountability is nowhere to be
OL,12,Fseen. I will push for real action on
OL,13,Fhousing by unlocking development,
OL,14,Fcutting red tape, and making sure
OL,15,Fhomes are built for locals, not just
OL,16,Finvestors.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I am passionate about restoring
OL,7,Ffairness - tackling wasteful spending,
OL,8,Fchallenging a bloated system, and
OL,9,Fensuring taxpayers see value for
OL,10,Fmoney. I will stand firm on law and
OL,11,Forder, back our police, and demand
OL,12,Fhigher standards across the board.
OL,14,F"This isn't about empty promises or
OL,15,Fpolitical games. It's about common
OL,16,Fsense, responsibility, and leadership
OL,17,Fthat actually delivers. Guernsey
OL,18,Fdeserves representatives who say what
OL,19,Fthey mean and act on it. I'm standing
OL,20,Fto be exactly that."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,FRob Harnish
OL,8,F"My views on specific issues are at
OL,9,Fwww.harnish.gg, but no policy will
OL,10,Fsucceed while our Civil Service
OL,11,Fculture continues to undermine best
OL,12,Fpractice. I am standing in this
OL,13,Felection because that culture needs
OL,14,Freform.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
