PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"The evidence is overwhelming. After
OL,7,Fchallenging failings for nearly a
OL,8,Fdecade, Families for Culture Change
OL,9,Ftold the Guernsey Press their voices
OL,10,Fwere "suppressed or silenced." Add to
OL,11,Fthat the #18m MyGov case, the #30m
OL,12,Fhospital redevelopment case, the #42m
OL,13,FIT transformation case.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"The iceberg is clearly visible.This
OL,7,FJanuary, the States mandated
OL,8,Fstructural reform because senior
OL,9,Fmanagement was "almost impossible to
OL,10,Fhold to account." Structural reform
OL,11,Fhas been tried before, but it has
OL,12,Ffailed every time because the problem
OL,13,Fis not structural; it is cultural.I
OL,14,Fhave helped to drive culture change
OL,15,Fbefore - at an Oxford college, in an
OL,16,FIsland school, and most recently with
OL,17,Fa Guernsey charity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"You put constituency work first. You
OL,7,Fpursue truth with courage, justice
OL,8,Fwith integrity, and community with
OL,9,Fcompassion. You lead by example.I know
OL,10,Fwhat to do and how to do it. I am
OL,11,Fasking you to give me the chance.
OL,13,F"My ears, your voice."
OL,15,FSam Haskins
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I am standing for election because I
OL,7,Fcare deeply about the future of
OL,8,FGuernsey, and I believe we need a
OL,9,Fstronger focus on accountability,
OL,10,Fsavings, and reducing the cost of
OL,11,Fliving.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"Over the past term, I've seen how
OL,7,Fdecisions are made and, just as
OL,8,Fimportantly, where the system falls
OL,9,Fshort. Too often, we identify the
OL,10,Fright problems but fail to follow
OL,11,Fthrough with effective, deliverable
OL,12,Fsolutions. Whether it's housing, the
OL,13,Fcost of living, or government
OL,14,Fspending, people are rightly asking
OL,15,Ffor better outcomes and greater
OL,16,Ftransparency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"My priorities are clear: driving down
OL,7,Funnecessary spending, improving
OL,8,Faccountability across government, and
OL,9,Ftackling the cost of living in a
OL,10,Fmeaningful way. That means asking
OL,11,Fdifficult questions, challenging poor
OL,12,Fvalue for money, and ensuring that
OL,13,Fpolicies actually deliver what they
OL,14,Fpromise.
OL,16,F"I also want to see real progress on
OL,17,Fhousing, both increasing supply and
OL,18,Fmaking it more accessible for local
OL,19,Fpeople, alongside a more disciplined,
OL,20,Fefficient approach to how government
OL,21,Foperates.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I'm standing to be part of that
OL,7,Fchange. I have experience, I
OL,8,Funderstand how the system works, and I
OL,9,Fcan add value immediately, even as a
OL,10,Fbackbencher, by asking the questions
OL,11,Fothers won't and pushing for better
OL,12,Fdecisions on behalf of islanders."
OL,14,FJulie-Anne Headington
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I am standing with Forward Guernsey
OL,7,Fso that we can deliver the change
OL,8,Frequired together - to build a fairer
OL,9,FGuernsey for all members of our
OL,10,Fcommunity: access to housing; fair
OL,11,Femployment and equality for all;
OL,12,Fimplementation of a fairer tax system,
OL,13,Foversight of capital projects,
OL,14,Fprotection of our natural environment;
OL,15,Faccess to affordable healthcare and an
OL,16,Feducation system in which our students
OL,17,Fcan thrive.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"Housing is the priority as it impacts
OL,7,Fall areas of the economy. Progress can
OL,8,Fonly be made if all stakeholders work
OL,9,Ftogether to facilitate the
OL,10,Favailability of land, including
OL,11,Fconstruction of property for first
OL,12,Ftime buyers along with emergency
OL,13,Fhousing to those facing homelessness.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"Having grown up in a State's house,
OL,7,Fand personally faced struggles as a
OL,8,Fsingle parent, I understand how
OL,9,Fdifficult it is to manage financially.
OL,10,FWith sheer determination, study and
OL,11,Fhard work, I was able to build and run
OL,12,Fa successful business in the insurance
OL,13,Findustry for 22 years.
OL,15,F"Today I work with Victim Support and
OL,16,Fwill ensure the implementation of the
OL,17,FVAWG taskforce is undertaken.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G17/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I have first hand experience of the
OL,7,Fchallenges islanders face and I am
OL,8,Fstanding because the Government should
OL,9,Fnever lose sight of the people it
OL,10,Fserves."
OL,12,FRoss Le Brun
OL,14,F"I believe I can offer something
OL,15,Fdifferent at a time when it is needed
OL,16,Fmost.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G18/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I did not come from a financially
OL,7,Fcomfortable background or well-
OL,8,Fconnected network. I grew up in social
OL,9,Fhousing, and my path has been built on
OL,10,Fhard work, determination, and
OL,11,Funderstanding the real challenges many
OL,12,Fpeople in our community face.
OL,14,F"I started my own business, growing it
OL,15,Fto employ nearly 400 local people over
OL,16,Ftime. That experience has given me a
OL,17,Fpractical understanding of jobs, the
OL,18,Feconomy, and what it takes to create
OL,19,Fopportunities for others.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G19/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38520
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I am the only candidate who chose to
OL,7,Fserve on ESS to be able to work on
OL,8,Faffordable housing. I did the full
OL,9,F4.5yrs as a non voting member tackling
OL,10,Fone of the island's most pressing
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,F"I'm not an opportunist.
OL,15,F"While others stepped back after the
OL,16,Fgeneral election, I kept pushing.
OL,17,FTalking with political committees
OL,18,Fpushing behind the scenes to directly
OL,19,Finfluence their priorities for this
OL,20,Fterm.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G20/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38521
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I am standing because I know have the
OL,7,Fdrive, experience, ideas and political
OL,8,Fcapability to make a meaningful
OL,9,Fdifference.
OL,11,F"I want to bring a fresh, grounded
OL,12,Fperspective to the States and focus on
OL,13,Fdelivering real results for our
OL,14,Fcommunity."
OL,16,FCarl Meerveld
OL,18,F"I am standing for re-election because
OL,19,Fthere are still things I am passionate
OL,20,Fabout which remain unresolved.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G21/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
