OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38522
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I oppose introducing GST and want the
OL,7,FStates to stop wasting millions
OL,8,Fthrough Civil Service mismanagement
OL,9,Fwhile generating revenue through
OL,10,Fexploiting our assets without
OL,11,Fincreasing personal taxes on our
OL,12,Falready overburdened population
OL,13,Fstruggling under our high cost of
OL,14,Fliving.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G22/43
