OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"We must focus on economic growth to
OL,7,Fgenerate additional corporate tax
OL,8,Frevenue and create higher-paying jobs.
OL,9,FGibraltar, a jurisdiction similar to
OL,10,Fours with half our population, is
OL,11,Fprojecting over 6% economic growth,
OL,12,Fwhile Guernsey projects 0.6%.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G23/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38524
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"We must also generate revenue from
OL,7,Fexploiting our assets. I have been
OL,8,Fchampioning the development of an
OL,9,Foffshore wind farm for years. Leasing
OL,10,Four seabed to a company that would
OL,11,Ffinance and build a wind farm large
OL,12,Fenough to not only cover Guernsey's
OL,13,Fneeds but also several million homes
OL,14,Fin the UK or France. Something that
OL,15,Fwould generate significantly more
OL,16,Frevenue for Guernsey, than GST, and
OL,17,Fcreate about 200 local, highly paid,
OL,18,Fnon-finance jobs, helping to diversify
OL,19,Fand grow our economy. While also
OL,20,Fsignificantly contributing to reducing
OL,21,Fcarbon emissions."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G24/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
