SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,FTamara Menteshvili
OL,8,F"I chose Guernsey as my home and I
OL,9,Fcare deeply about its future. I want
OL,10,Fto bring practical, responsible
OL,11,Fleadership to ensure our economy grows
OL,12,Fin a way that benefits everyone.
OL,14,F"A strong economy should be directed
OL,15,Fat improving people's lives. I support
OL,16,Fresponsible finances (no waste, no
OL,17,Funnecessary taxes).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G25/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
