FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38526
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"My aim is to make Guernsey affordable
OL,7,Ffor people to thrive by ensuring
OL,8,Fresponsible decision-making within
OL,9,FGovernment:
OL,11,F Support for employers ` they drive
OL,12,Ftax revenueJ Grow financial services
OL,13,Fintelligently, innovativelyJ Support
OL,14,Fnew sectors (film, marine/wellness
OL,15,Ftourism)
OL,17,F Urgent focus on first-time buyers/
OL,18,FrentersJ Island-wide urban planningJ
OL,19,FBetter use of States-owned assets
OL,21,FYoung People
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G26/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
