OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"My career has been focused upon
OL,7,Fbuilding strong foundations to support
OL,8,Feconomic growth, such as establishing
OL,9,Fthe stock exchange here, and serving
OL,10,Four community as Director, Les Bourgs.
OL,11,FI have worked at the highest levels of
OL,12,Ffinance and regulation on two
OL,13,Fcontinents, and understand how to grow
OL,14,Fan economy responsibly. But I am
OL,15,Fincreasingly concerned that we are not
OL,16,Ffocusing enough on delivery. I have
OL,17,Fsuccessfully delivered in the real
OL,18,Fworld and will bring that same
OL,19,Fapproach to government."
OL,21,FStephen Rouxel
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G28/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38529
SC,0029
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"My main priority is the economy and
OL,7,Fthe construction sector and house
OL,8,Fbuilding specifically. I have a
OL,9,Fconditional approach to any changes in
OL,10,FGuernsey's tax framework. I argue that
OL,11,Fincreases can only occur once
OL,12,Flivingstandard decline has stabilised,
OL,13,Fgovernment demonstrates cost
OL,14,Fdiscipline, and the Revenue Service is
OL,15,Foperationally ready or supported
OL,16,Fthrough outsourcing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G29/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38530
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I would only support GST Plus if
OL,7,Fpaired with reforms to tax caps for
OL,8,Fhighnetworth residents, requiring
OL,9,Fbeneficiaries to invest in Guernsey's
OL,10,Fstartups, SMEs or housing through a
OL,11,Fqualifying investment fund. I propose
OL,12,Fexpanding the Guernsey Enterprise
OL,13,FInvestment Scheme and revitalising the
OL,14,Fentrepreneurial ecosystem. With local
OL,15,Fcapital into local businesses
OL,16,Ftargeting construction, housebuilding,
OL,17,Ftechnology and the arts.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G30/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38531
SC,0031
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"To safeguard the economy, I call for
OL,7,Fa mandatory "tax gateway" assessment
OL,8,Fto ensure households and business can
OL,9,Fafford the change. I also propose
OL,10,Finvestigating new monetary policy, by
OL,11,Fexploring alternative currency
OL,12,Farrangements.
OL,14,F"I want to see a review of all
OL,15,Fcommittee activities, categorising
OL,16,Fthem as critical, important, or "nice
OL,17,Fto have". I also call operational
OL,18,Freforms within the Civil Service,
OL,19,Fincluding restructuring, exploring new
OL,20,Ftechnology, and improving internal
OL,21,Fprocess development.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G31/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38532
SC,0032
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"Proposals for the benefits trap,
OL,7,Fstrengthening air and sea
OL,8,Fconnectivity, and supporting tourism
OL,9,Fgrowth.
OL,11,FFor full details please visit
OL,12,Fwww.stephenrouxel.com."
OL,14,FNikki Symons
OL,16,F"I am standing in this by-election to
OL,17,Foffer an experienced, thoughtful and
OL,18,Fpractical voice for Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G32/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38533
SC,0033
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I understand how government works and
OL,7,Fthe importance of making clear,
OL,8,Fbalanced decisions. I won't make
OL,9,Funrealistic promises. Instead, I will
OL,10,Ffocus on where I can make a real and
OL,11,Fimmediate contribution asking the
OL,12,Fright questions, challenging where
OL,13,Fneeded, and helping to move things
OL,14,Fforward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G33/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38534
SC,0034
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"My priorities reflect the issues
OL,7,Fpeople raise most. Housing is a major
OL,8,Fconcern, and we need to increase
OL,9,Fsupply and make better use of existing
OL,10,Fproperties so younger generations and
OL,11,Fworking households can build their
OL,12,Ffuture here.
OL,14,F"We also need to take responsible
OL,15,Fdecisions on public finances. Guernsey
OL,16,Ffaces a structural deficit, and doing
OL,17,Fnothing is not an option. Any changes,
OL,18,Fincluding GST+, must be fair, balanced
OL,19,Fand clearly explained.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G34/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38535
SC,0035
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"A strong economy underpins everything
OL,7,Felse, so I will support local
OL,8,Fbusinesses, encourage innovation, and
OL,9,Fensure Guernsey remains competitive
OL,10,Fand future-ready.
OL,12,F"Alongside this, we need to improve
OL,13,Fhow government delivers by
OL,14,Fstrengthening civil service
OL,15,Fefficiency, improving accountability,
OL,16,Fmanaging projects effectively, and
OL,17,Fensuring they are delivered on time
OL,18,Fand within budget.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G35/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38536
SC,0036
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"Above all, I will listen, communicate
OL,7,Fclearly, and work hard to represent
OL,8,Fyour views."
OL,10,FAndy Taylor
OL,12,F"In election campaigns, it's easy to
OL,13,Fidentify problems and propose
OL,14,Fsolutions. The hard part is turning
OL,15,Fthose ideas into something workable
OL,16,Fwithin the financial, legal and
OL,17,Fpractical constraints that exist. I
OL,18,Fthink Guernsey deserves more honesty
OL,19,Fabout how decisions are made - and how
OL,20,Fdifficult they can be to deliver.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G36/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38537
SC,0037
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"That's where I believe the focus
OL,7,Fshould be.
OL,9,F"Whether it's housing, care, or wider
OL,10,Ffinancial policy, the challenge is not
OL,11,Frecognising the issue - it's
OL,12,Funderstanding the detail, testing
OL,13,Fassumptions, and working through how a
OL,14,Fsolution can actually be delivered.
OL,15,FWithout that, even the best intentions
OL,16,Fwon't lead to meaningful change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G37/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38538
SC,0038
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I don't shy away from difficult
OL,7,Fconversations or inconvenient facts,
OL,8,Feven where they challenge my own
OL,9,Fposition. I believe we need more grown-
OL,10,Fup conversations about the Island's
OL,11,Ffuture. My priorities lie in housing,
OL,12,Flong-term care, and how we fund them
OL,13,Fsustainably.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G38/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38539
SC,0039
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"Having formed, run and sold
OL,7,Fbusinesses over the past decade, I
OL,8,Funderstand what it takes to turn an
OL,9,Fidea into something deliverable. I've
OL,10,Fexperienced both commercial success
OL,11,Fand setbacks, and have learned as much
OL,12,Ffrom the difficult periods as the
OL,13,Fsuccessful ones. The approach I bring
OL,14,Fis practical, considered, and focused
OL,15,Fon outcomes that can genuinely be
OL,16,Fdelivered."
OL,18,FJonathan Wilson
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G39/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38540
SC,0040
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"Guernsey is a remarkable place, with
OL,7,Fnatural advantages that most places
OL,8,Fcan only dream about. Financial
OL,9,Fsophistication, autonomy, a contained
OL,10,Fand manageable scale, and one of the
OL,11,Fmost powerful tidal energy resources
OL,12,Fon Earth sitting just a few miles
OL,13,Foffshore.
OL,15,F"What it has often lacked is a
OL,16,Fgovernment structure to think clearly
OL,17,Fabout the long term and to act
OL,18,Fcoherently across departmental
OL,19,Fboundaries before problems become
OL,20,Fcrises.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G40/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38541
SC,0041
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"The black hole deficit did not appear
OL,7,Fovernight, the housing shortage did
OL,8,Fnot arrive without warning, and the
OL,9,Fdependence on a single subsea cable
OL,10,Ffor 90% of our energy was always going
OL,11,Fto be a strategic vulnerability. These
OL,12,Fare not separate failures, they are
OL,13,Fthe same institutional problem,
OL,14,Fexpressed in different places from a
OL,15,FStates that has been making short-term
OL,16,Fdecisions inside departmental silos
OL,17,Ffor a generation, and now we are
OL,18,Fpaying heavily to fix things than
OL,19,Fshould never have gone this wrong.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G41/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38542
SC,0042
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1777050358
OL,3,CWhat do Guernsey's by-election
OL,4,Ccandidates stand for?
OL,6,F"I'm Jonathan Wilson and I'm standing
OL,7,Fbecause I believe that fixing how the
OL,8,FStates thinks, plans, and coordinates,
OL,9,Fis the precondition to solving
OL,10,Feverything else, whether that's energy
OL,11,Findependence, housing, or fiscal
OL,12,Fsustainability for a Guernsey that is
OL,13,Fmore self-sufficient and more
OL,14,Fprosperous for the generations that
OL,15,Ffollow ours."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G42/43
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
